{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 轻量 router 选少量 experts + shared lookup + expert-local top-k lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前最高优先级的 hetero-MoE 结构“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head / local top-k”在约 0.28x total_cost 下，是否能优于现有 0.28x-0.32x 低成本 frontier 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下接近或优于当前 0.28x-0.32x anchors，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，测试 shared scorer 还能否继续左移而不明显掉质。","如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则不要继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做局部扫参，下一轮切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 做同 recipe 的 matched architecture probe。","如果结果异常差且与历史 r141 同向，可把“shared low-rank basis + routed local head”在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，转回别的未充分验证结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=794624，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=1187840，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.28，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是对当前 operator hint 明确优先的 hetero-MoE 方向做 matched-cost 重验，不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 上做旧 family 局部微调。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我没有返回代码改动，因为当前高优先级候选 family 已经落盘且可运行；本轮更需要的是用当前低成本 anchor recipe 做一次干净的 matched architecture swap。选择这条线而不是继续调 `lowrank_expert_*`，是因为运行时提示已明确把“shared experts + routed experts，尤其 shared low-rank basis + expert-local top-k”列为当前最值得补的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号；但那些结果主要来自更早的 112/128 recipe，本轮用当前 `K=96, latents_per_expert=224` 的低成本配方重验，归因更直接。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.28x 低成本带的 matched hetero-MoE 结构探针，直接验证当前最高优先级方向“shared low-rank basis + routed expert local top-k”是否能形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。","touched_files":[]}

